      "rationale": "Bilinear elastic-plastic constitutive model for titanium alloy Ti-6Al-4V is supported by published material characterization data. Penalty-based frictionless contact at screw-rod interface justified by sensitivity study showing <3% QoI change versus frictional contact. Geometric fidelity confirmed against CAD drawings. Gradation 3 achieved."
