      "rationale": "Testing conducted under a single ASTM F1717 load configuration (compression-bending at 5 mm/min crosshead displacement). Only one load rate evaluated; multi-rate or multi-angle coverage not achieved. Environmental conditions (23±2°C, ambient humidity) documented. Gradation 2 achieved against required Gradation 3 — this factor does not meet the required level."
